# Package Management Module
#
# Simple language package manager - install, build, test, and distribute packages.
# Provides manifest parsing, dependency resolution, version management, and distribution.
#
# Public API:
#   - use app.package.main.{package_main}
#   - use app.package.build.{build_package}
#   - use app.package.install.{install_package}
#   - use app.package.dist.{create_dist}
#   - use app.package.manifest.{PackageManifest}
#   - use app.package.types.{Package, PackageVersion, Dependency}
#
# Internal Components:
#   - Manifest and lockfile management
#   - Semantic versioning
#   - Path resolution
#   - FFI testing (all_ffi_test, complete_ffi_test, simple_ffi_test)
#   - Integration testing

# All submodules are automatically available through the module system.
# Package management is evolving toward a registry-based system with
# centralized package hosting and dependency resolution.
